lead_paragraph: Teana Muldrow had season highs of 21 points and 10 rebounds and No. 19 West Virginia beat East Carolina 79-47 on Wednesday at the Savannah Invitational for the undefeated Mountaineers' sixth straight victory.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 West Virginia Women Defeat East Carolina 79-47
